content:
if all AI crypto players unite, we might have some sort of an super agent actually pretty soon: 

- private with 
@nillionnetwork

- ip-preserving with 
@StoryProtocol

- specialized with 
@OpenledgerHQ

- verifiable with 
@eigenlayer


+ so many others

best thing happening to this space is going away from technical jargon 

verifiability from 
@eigenlayer
, expressivity from 
@fluentxyz
, blind computation from 
@nillionnetwork
 or specialized ai by 
@OpenledgerHQ


this is so much better and understandable than crazy new shiny words

my list: 
@megaeth_labs
 and especially the apps in its ecosystem. they manage to have new potential viral use cases, just need to see in practice
@fluentxyz
 and expressivity come to life. want to see what putting all tools from all ecosystems looks like in practice

ethereum's

the main point of chain abstraction? fixing the broken user experience

cool part? it is *already* real
@UseUniversalX
 lets users trade onchain with the feel of a centralized exchange
@KintoXYZ
 and 
@SOCKETProtocol
 let users swap on mainnet and a few L2s right from Kinto.

and

"but bro, user experience is better"

well not anymore, hyperliquid has the same if not a better experience for perps

same goes for spot, you can have exactly the same user interface from 
@UseUniversalX
 or 
@infinex_app
